      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOT RUBY (5) has a strong winning strike-rate this journey here having won two of four starts. Recorded a one length win (19.96) in a TG1-4W last time at this track. Expected to be in the finish. ADHANA LAYLA (1) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Finished in the money last time though when second (23.13) at Gawler. Has a strong record here at this journey including two wins. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Can feature again. GOLDIE RUSTY (7) has been hard to follow lately, running fifth (20.04) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Expected to bounce back to best. SOKAI (2) must be respected at his pet distance.",
